她以前住这儿
{\fs11}Her former residence.{\r}

796
00:48:10,630 --> 00:48:12,970
你现在可以自己买酒了 阿尔菲 杜利特
{\fs11}You can buy your own drinks now, Alfie Doolittle.{\r}

797
00:48:13,180 --> 00:48:15,010
你可真是掉进黄油桶里了
{\fs11}Fallen into a tub of butter, you have.{\r}

798
00:48:15,220 --> 00:48:18,220
- 你在说什么？ - 你女儿 伊莉莎
{\fs11}- What are you talking about? - Your daughter, Eliza.{\r}

799
00:48:18,430 --> 00:48:20,310
你真走运 阿尔菲 杜利特
{\fs11}You're a lucky man, Alfie Doolittle.{\r}

800
00:48:20,520 --> 00:48:22,140
嗯 伊莉莎怎么了？
{\fs11}Well, what about Eliza?{\r}

801
00:48:22,350 --> 00:48:26,110
噢！他还不知道呢 她自己的父亲都还不知道
{\fs11}Oh! He don't know. Her own father and he don't know.{\r}

802
00:48:26,400 --> 00:48:29,440
