807
00:48:41,370 --> 00:48:43,460
她要把她的东西全都送到
{\fs11}She wants her things sent over.{\r}

808
00:48:43,670 --> 00:48:46,750
温珀街27A号
{\fs11}To 27A Wimpole Street,{\r}

809
00:48:46,960 --> 00:48:49,050
由希金斯教授转交...
{\fs11}care of Professor Higgins.{\r}

810
00:48:49,250 --> 00:48:50,380
