{\fs11}[ALFIE LAUGHS]{\r}

814
00:48:59,310 --> 00:49:00,890
“不过”她在信里说
{\fs11}"But," she says,{\r}

815
00:49:01,100 --> 00:49:05,190
“衣物什么的就不必送过来了”
{\fs11}"never mind about sending any clothes."{\r}

816
00:49:05,400 --> 00:49:07,810
[所有人都在笑]
{\fs11}[ALL LAUGHING]{\r}

817
00:49:08,020 --> 00:49:10,860
我早就知道她有出息
{\fs11}I knew she had a career in front of her.{\r}

818
00:49:11,070 --> 00:49:13,400
哈利老弟 我们得一起庆祝下
{\fs11}Harry boy, we're in for a booze-up.{\r}

819
00:49:13,610 --> 00:49:17,240
这回阿尔弗雷德 P 杜利特可走运了 <font color=#FF7F00>[阿尔菲是阿尔弗雷德的简称]</font>
{\fs11}The sun is shining on Alfred P. Doolittle.{\r}

